# Signal Strait Labs Project Rules

## Tech Stack Standards
- Framework: Next.js 15+ (App Router, strict TypeScript)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4+ utility syntax
- Infrastructure: Serverless, edge-optimized deployment on Cloudflare Pages

## Core Styling Conventions
- Theme: Ultra-premium luxury dark design system
- Primary Background: #01081b (or utility class `.luxury-bg-gradient`)
- Accent Colors: Pure Digital Blue (`#1a59cc`), Premium Golden (`#C5A059`)
- Text Gradient: Always utilize the `.text-gold-gradient` utility class for high-impact hero headings.

## Code Constraints
- Maintain Server Components by default for SEO/GEO discoverability.
- Only add 'use client' at the very top of files requiring explicit interactive client hooks (e.g., state, event listeners).
- Never pass interactive event functions directly inside non-client layout structures.